---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="세무회계본 | 강남 수서 세무사 - 상속·증여·양도 전문"
  description="강남 수서역 세무회계본. 14년 경력 천아름 대표세무사의 상속세, 증여세, 양도소득세 전문 컨설팅. 수서역 3번 출구 직결."
  canonical="https://taxbon.com/"
  currentPage="home"
>

<!-- 2. 메인 히어로 슬라이드 (자동/수동) -->
    <section id="home" class="relative h-[650px] bg-gray-900 overflow-hidden pt-20">
        <!-- 슬라이드 1: 천아름 대표 -->
        <div class="hero-slide active">
            <div class="absolute inset-0">
                <img src="/images/사무실전경.jpg" alt="세무회계본 전경" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-navy-900/95 via-navy-900/70 to-transparent"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 h-full flex items-center">
                <div class="max-w-2xl text-white pt-10">
                    <div class="inline-block border border-gold-500 text-gold-500 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-6 tracking-wide">
                        천아름 세무사
                    </div>
                    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
                        상속·증여·양도,<br>
                        <span class="text-gold-500">가치를 지키는 솔루션</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed font-light">
                        14년차 조세 전문가가 고객님의 소중한 자산을 지켜드립니다.<br>
                        복잡한 재산세제, 세무회계본이 가장 확실한 해답입니다.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap">
                        <a href="#contact" class="bg-gold-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-gold-600 transition shadow-lg inline-flex items-center">
                            상담 예약하기 <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="ml-2 w-4 h-4"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="/intake" class="border-2 border-gold-400 text-gold-400 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-gold-500 hover:text-white hover:border-gold-500 transition shadow-lg inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                            📋 준비서류 확인
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 슬라이드 2: 권창호 자문 -->
        <div class="hero-slide">
            <div class="absolute inset-0">
                <img src="/images/20251211_163103.jpg" alt="비즈니스 미팅" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-navy-900/95 via-navy-900/70 to-transparent"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 h-full flex items-center">
                <div class="max-w-2xl text-white pt-10">
                    <div class="inline-block border border-green-400 text-green-400 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-6 tracking-wide">
                        권창호 세무사
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
                        개인사업자 및 요식업 특화<br>
                        <span class="text-green-400">맞춤형 절세 전략</span>
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed font-light">
                        세무사와 공인중개사 자격을 모두 갖춘 15년 경력 전문가.<br>
                        사장님의 사업 성공을 위한 든든한 파트너가 되겠습니다.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <a href="#contact" class="bg-green-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-green-700 transition shadow-lg inline-flex items-center">
                            기장 문의하기 <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="ml-2 w-4 h-4"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 슬라이드 변환 버튼 -->
        <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 flex space-x-3 z-20">
            <button onclick="manualSwitchHero(0)" class="hero-dot w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gold-500 transition-all duration-300 ring-2 ring-transparent focus:ring-white"></button>
            <button onclick="manualSwitchHero(1)" class="hero-dot w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gray-600 transition-all duration-300 ring-2 ring-transparent focus:ring-white"></button>
        </div>
    </section>


    <!-- 3. 전문가 소개 (1명씩 확실한 슬라이드) -->
    <section id="about" class="py-24 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <span class="text-gold-500 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">Specialist</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-800 mt-2">전문가 소개</h2>
            </div>

            <!-- 슬라이더 컨테이너: 트랙 방식으로 한 명씩 표시 -->
            <div class="relative bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-gray-100 min-h-[480px] overflow-hidden expert-slider">
                <!-- 이전/다음 버튼 -->
                <button class="absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-20 p-3 rounded-full bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-md hover:bg-white/60 transition-all border border-white/30">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <button class="absolute right-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-20 p-3 rounded-full bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-md hover:bg-white/60 transition-all border border-white/30">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                </button>

                <div class="expert-track h-full">
                    <!-- 전문가 1: 천아름 대표세무사 -->
                    <div class="expert-item expert-slide-fade h-full">
                        <div class="w-full md:w-3/12 relative bg-gray-100 min-h-[280px] md:min-h-0 md:h-auto flex items-center justify-center p-4">
                            <img src="/images/car.jpg" alt="천아름 대표세무사" class="w-full max-w-[200px] h-auto object-cover object-top rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                            <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap">
                                <span class="bg-navy-800/70 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold shadow-lg">#마을세무사</span>
                                <span class="bg-gold-500/70 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold shadow-lg">#대표</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-full md:w-9/12 p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center bg-white">
                            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">천아름 <span class="text-lg text-gray-500 font-normal">세무사</span></h3>
                            <p class="text-gold-500 font-bold mb-6">상속·증여·양도 / 재산세제 전문</p>
                            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-navy-800 mb-4 flex items-center text-base"><i data-lucide="award" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-gold-500"></i>주요 경력 및 이력</h4>
                                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-left">
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gold-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>2011년 제48회 세무사 자격 취득</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gold-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>국립창원대학교 세무학과 졸업</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gold-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>前 세무법인 하나/동광 근무</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gold-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>前 세무법인 에이블 파트너</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gold-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>現 세무법인 성진(광주) 법인세 자문 / 會 회계법인 한서(종로) 세무 자문</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-navy-800 rounded-full mr-2"></span><strong class="text-navy-800 font-extrabold">2017년~현재 세무회계본 대표세무사</strong></li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mr-2"></span>서울지방세무사회 감리위원 (2021.05~2023.05)</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mr-2"></span>서울시 마을세무사 (2022.01~현재) 표창장4572호</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 전문가 2: 권창호 자문 세무사 -->
                    <div class="expert-item expert-slide-fade h-full">
                        <div class="w-full md:w-3/12 relative bg-gray-100 min-h-[280px] md:min-h-0 md:h-auto flex items-center justify-center p-4">
                                <img src="/images/bf88eca3cee1a.png" alt="권창호 자문 세무사" class="w-full max-w-[200px] h-auto object-cover object-center rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                                <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap">
                                    <span class="bg-gray-700/70 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold shadow-lg">#공인중개사</span>
                                    <span class="bg-green-600/70 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold shadow-lg">#세무사</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        <div class="w-full md:w-9/12 p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center bg-white">
                            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">권창호 <span class="text-lg text-gray-500 font-normal">세무사</span></h3>
                            <p class="text-green-600 font-bold mb-6">개인사업자 / 요식업 / 부동산 자문</p>
                            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-navy-800 mb-4 flex items-center text-base"><i data-lucide="award" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-600"></i>주요 경력 및 이력</h4>
                                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-left">
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>2010년 제47회 세무사 합격</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span><strong class="text-green-700 font-extrabold">2022년 제32회 공인중개사 합격</strong></li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>단국대학교 회계학과 졸업</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mr-2"></span>용산세무서 신고도우미 / 국세청 고객만족센터 근무</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mr-2"></span>前 세무법인 창조 / 디딤세무회계 근무</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mr-2"></span>중랑구 영세납세자지원단 나눔세무사</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mr-2"></span>중랑세무서 민생지원소통추진단 외부위원</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 전문가 3: 최지훈 감정평가사 -->
                    <div class="expert-item expert-slide-fade h-full">
                        <div class="w-full md:w-3/12 relative bg-gray-100 min-h-[280px] md:min-h-0 md:h-auto flex items-center justify-center p-4">
                                <img src="/images/KakaoTalk_20260205_143448097.jpg" alt="최지훈 감정평가사" class="w-full max-w-[200px] h-auto object-cover object-center rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                                <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap">
                                    <span class="bg-amber-600/70 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold shadow-lg">#감정평가사</span>
                                    <span class="bg-amber-800/70 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold shadow-lg">#이사</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        <div class="w-full md:w-9/12 p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center bg-white">
                            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">최지훈 <span class="text-lg text-gray-500 font-normal">감정평가사</span></h3>
                            <p class="text-amber-600 font-bold mb-6">부동산 감정평가 / 기준가격 자문</p>
                            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-navy-800 mb-4 flex items-center text-base"><i data-lucide="award" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-amber-600"></i>주요 경력 및 이력</h4>
                                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-left">
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-amber-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>2016년 감정평가사 자격 취득</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-amber-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>고려대학교 화학과 졸업</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mr-2"></span>前 중앙감정평가법인 본사 근무</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mr-2"></span>前 삼일감정평가법인 본사 근무</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-amber-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span><strong class="text-amber-700 font-extrabold">現 명문감정평가법인 본사 이사</strong></li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-amber-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>2025~2026년 지방세연구원 기타물건 기준가격 용역자문</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 전문가 4: 김진범 공인회계사 -->
                    <div class="expert-item expert-slide-fade h-full">
                        <div class="w-full md:w-3/12 relative bg-gray-100 min-h-[280px] md:min-h-0 md:h-auto flex items-center justify-center p-4">
                                <img src="/images/kjb.png" alt="김진범 공인회계사" class="w-full max-w-[200px] h-auto object-cover object-center rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                                <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap">
                                    <span class="bg-indigo-600/70 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold shadow-lg">#공인회계사</span>
                                    <span class="bg-indigo-800/70 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold shadow-lg">#Partner</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        <div class="w-full md:w-9/12 p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center bg-white">
                            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">김진범 <span class="text-lg text-gray-500 font-normal">공인회계사</span></h3>
                            <p class="text-indigo-600 font-bold mb-6">회계감사 / 가치평가 / M&A 자문</p>
                            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-navy-800 mb-4 flex items-center text-base"><i data-lucide="award" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-indigo-600"></i>주요 경력 및 이력</h4>
                                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-left">
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>2007년 제42회 공인회계사 자격 취득</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>단국대학교 경영학과 졸업</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mr-2"></span>前 삼정회계법인 근무 / 前 광교회계법인 근무</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span><strong class="text-indigo-700 font-extrabold">現 한서회계법인 이사(Partner)</strong></li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mr-2"></span>前 농림축산식품 연구개발사업 이의신청위원회 심의위원</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mr-2"></span>前 19대 대통령선거 중앙선관위 공정재무감사 특별위원</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mr-2"></span>前 양천구 지방보조금 심의위원</li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span><strong class="text-indigo-600">주요업무: 회계감사, 실사 및 가치평가, M&A 및 투자자문</strong></li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 페이징 도트 -->
                <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 z-20 flex space-x-3">
                    <button onclick="goToExpert(0)" class="expert-dot w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gold-500 transition-all"></button>
                    <button onclick="goToExpert(1)" class="expert-dot w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gray-300 transition-all"></button>
                    <button onclick="goToExpert(2)" class="expert-dot w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gray-300 transition-all"></button>
                    <button onclick="goToExpert(3)" class="expert-dot w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gray-300 transition-all"></button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 4. 주요 서비스 (카드 형태 - 요청대로 유지) -->
    <section id="services" class="py-24 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <span class="text-gold-500 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">Services</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-800 mt-2 mb-4">세무회계본의 전문 서비스</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600">각 분야 최고의 전문가가 1:1 맞춤형 세무 관리를 제공합니다.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- 서비스 1: 상속/증여/양도 (가장 먼저) -->
